creator: PicTime
descriptionHtml:
PicTime is the most authentic and fun social network!

How does it work?
With PicTime, you can only take photos (or videos) and upload them when a friend request it to you.

Whaaaaat ??? Yes, yes, only when you receive a PicTime moment (Push Notification) you can access the camera and take the photos you want.

So - PicTime will be full of real-time, real-life, funny or awe inspiring photos... what you see in PicTime, is happening. It's authentic and without limits...
descriptionShort: PicTime is the most authentic and fun social network!

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: Now it's posible to send video request! 📹

title: PicTime

creator: PicTime
descriptionHtml:
Pictime is a real social network to chat for free with your friends and meet new people sharing REAL moments of your day to day life, ordinary as life itself! 

Aren't you tired of the fake looks of social networks? Stop looking for the perfect time, the best outfit and the ideal environment to impress your friends (or flirts), and change the rules of the game by tempting with a Pictime. 

In Pictime, you can share photos privately with whomever you choose with the additional incentive that they”ll eventually disappear, leaving no trace of the exchange. Real-time, sporadic and un-prepared images... what you see is what they see. It’s authentic and has no limits!

Sharing with PicTime is easy and fun. You can chat for free with your friends or meet new people and ask them to send a photo or video to you. That's your "PicTime" moment. The recipient only has 5 minutes to open the camera and take a picture or video. No filters or pre-preparations, just a REAL shot. You too can receive these requests and answer them whenever you want with photos or videos. This is called sending a "One Way". Your One Way PicTimes are private, only the person you send them to will be able to see them for a limited time.

But beware! They can also respond to you with a PicTime "Swap" and you can only unlock the photo or video by sending another one in return - exchange your moments in a different way!

Leave behind the ghosts of other social networks, PicTime gives you the opportunity to meet REAL people, with no filters! Do you dare?
descriptionShort: Chat for free and meet new people sharing REAL moments, be yourself!
